DarkMouse::
She saw on the scanners that there were bots outside, "Hey, BossBot, 
Drillbit, we got a few bots outside. Want me to let them in?"
She didn't wait for a reply and opened the door for them. She opened 
her link,"Hey boys, welcome to our humble base. I'd come in but stay 
in the main hall if I was you guys. I got the autoguns on you. So 
stay put untill the leader gets to you guys. Got it?"
